{"tid":2107848,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"路透社消息：美國將終止與中國的審計協議  加強壓制在美上市中國企業","createTime":"2020-07-14T06:58:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-14T07:40:32.000Z","uid":7542,"like":27,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"727a52f8b497645fa978d8ff634c964753af7d46","tid":2107848,"uid":7542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T06:58:38.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong>希望國家反制 </strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n路透社引述美國國務院一名資深官員表示，美國計劃取消與中國審計當局在2013年簽署的協議，<strong>有關做法可能預示對在美上市的中國企業進行更廣泛的壓制</strong>。<br />\n<br />\n報道指，<strong>協議主要讓美國審計監督機構建立查閱檔案流程，可翻查相關資料</strong>，但美國長久以來指中國未能批准有關要求。 美國負責經濟增長、能源和環境的官員指，由於缺乏透明度促使政府官員為盡快退出協議舖路。另一位政府官員稱正在考慮終止備忘錄，又指白宮參與討論。 <br />\n<br />\n白宮、中國駐美國大使館及監督機構未回覆消息。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1537643-20200714.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1537643-20200714.htm&d=nqzd6QM3TLyrPp4uhCfCn7CEdHrHTgyyxjjYSTVVVd4%3D&h=230f7fb7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1537643-20200714.htm&h=32940490\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1537643-20200714.htm</a>"},{"pid":"d53b01882f014e2e36b6e96dbf802fb135ef9976","tid":2107848,"uid":7542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T07:00:04.000Z","msg":"<strong>政府建制派聯手日日喺度嘈民主派初選違反國安法，又或者點樣點樣操控選舉。<br />\n<br />\n咩叫操控選舉？唔該每個人睇一睇：<br />\n</strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/0ggBftnYDQ4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F0ggBftnYDQ4&d=nqzd6QM3TLyrPp4uhCfCn7CEdHrHTgyyxjjYSTVVVd4%3D&h=b0fdc8c9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/0ggBftnYDQ4</a>"},{"pid":"35393b26732f0ed9daaee15fa706b26051f38cb3","tid":2107848,"uid":144626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T07:00:27.000Z","msg":"一浪接